  "id": "BIT-argo-workflows-2026-42183",
  "summary": "Argo Workflows: SSO RBAC Delegation Nil Pointer Dereference DoS (gatekeeper.go)",
  "details": "Argo Workflows is an open source container-native workflow engine for orchestrating parallel jobs on Kubernetes. From version 4.0.0 to before version 4.0.5, a nil pointer dereference in server/auth/gatekeeper.go rbacAuthorization() causes a panic (denial of service) for SSO users whose claims match a namespace-level RBAC rule but not an SSO-namespace rule, when SSO_DELEGATE_RBAC_TO_NAMESPACE=true. This issue has been patched in version 4.0.5.",
  "aliases": [
